1
00:01:32,300 --> 00:01:39,840
[Better Halves]

2
00:01:40,340 --> 00:01:43,009
[Episode 8]

3
00:01:50,460 --> 00:01:51,270
Lu,

4
00:01:51,310 --> 00:01:52,570
Li Ang came prepared.

5
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:54,160
The tea-spilling plan failed.

6
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:56,470
Ms. Deng will deliver
the Information Card tomorrow.

7
00:01:56,470 --> 00:01:57,470
What should we do?

8
00:01:57,479 --> 00:01:58,410
Don't worry, Ke.

9
00:01:58,700 --> 00:01:59,870
You go stop Miss Shen

10
00:01:59,890 --> 00:02:00,950
and bring her back to watch the show.

11
00:02:00,950 --> 00:02:02,810
This time, I'll handle it myself.

12
00:02:02,980 --> 00:02:04,180
I promise it'll work.

13
00:02:08,289 --> 00:02:09,340
Lu.

14
00:02:11,630 --> 00:02:12,720
Be careful.

15
00:02:13,150 --> 00:02:14,880
Don't take unnecessary risks.

16
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:25,880
She's Miss Shen, right?

17
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:26,870
Miss Shen.

18
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,180
I...

19
00:02:28,310 --> 00:02:30,990
Tongyun, don't feel pressured.

20
00:02:31,190 --> 00:02:33,630
I just don't want you
to end up with the wrong person.

21
00:02:33,630 --> 00:02:36,070
Rumors say General Li is quite...

22
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:42,730
Perhaps someone spread the rumors
out of jealousy.

23
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:46,120
As long as he's not a bad person,
that's enough.

24
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:49,190
Tongyun, be careful on your way.

25
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,670
I'm leaving.

26
00:02:55,850 --> 00:02:57,270
Miss Shen, wait.

27
00:02:57,630 --> 00:02:59,120
I have something to tell you.

28
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:01,190
What else do you want to say? Go ahead.

29
00:03:02,150 --> 00:03:04,810
General Li is violent and cruel
and kills innocent people.

30
00:03:04,810 --> 00:03:07,810
You truly haven't heard
even a whisper of such things?

31
00:03:08,030 --> 00:03:08,910
Miss Shi,

32
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:09,750
I thought you were someone

33
00:03:09,750 --> 00:03:11,750
who could see beyond common prejudice

34
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:13,430
and wouldn't blindly believe rumors.

35
00:03:13,430 --> 00:03:14,360
I never expected

36
00:03:14,870 --> 00:03:16,400
you'd be just like the rest.

37
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:17,940
In the capital,

38
00:03:17,970 --> 00:03:20,290
rumors about me being boy-crazy
are everywhere.

39
00:03:20,290 --> 00:03:22,020
I know better than anyone

40
00:03:22,190 --> 00:03:24,560
what it feels like
to live under a storm of rumors.

41
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,690
I only trust what I see with my own eyes.

42
00:03:27,190 --> 00:03:29,040
You trust what you see with your own eyes.

43
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:30,440
I have no issue with that.

44
00:03:31,130 --> 00:03:32,490
If he truly has a gentle nature,

45
00:03:32,490 --> 00:03:33,890
he should be consistent.

46
00:03:34,150 --> 00:03:35,370
Why don't you go back with me

47
00:03:35,370 --> 00:03:36,829
to see for yourself again?

48
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,360
If he really is a good man,

49
00:03:38,900 --> 00:03:41,930
I'll give up the idea
of finding someone else for you.

50
00:03:46,329 --> 00:03:48,620
Fine, I'll go back with you

51
00:03:49,050 --> 00:03:50,850
so that you can give up your idea.

52
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,680
Damn woman!

53
00:03:54,930 --> 00:03:57,150
How did Shen Tongyun know
such a lowly, penniless scholar?

54
00:03:57,150 --> 00:03:57,980
What right does he have

55
00:03:57,980 --> 00:03:59,710
to enter my private room and sit here

56
00:03:59,710 --> 00:04:01,640
drinking tea and chatting with me?

57
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:02,840
Yes.

58
00:04:03,030 --> 00:04:04,830
General, please don't be angry.

59
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:05,910
Wang Ren

60
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,360
was brought here by Shi Fa'ke

61
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:09,290
to disgust you on purpose.

62
00:04:09,430 --> 00:04:10,150
Fortunately,

63
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:12,590
I knew
Shi Fa'ke wouldn't give up so easily

64
00:04:12,710 --> 00:04:14,990
and discussed countermeasures with you.

65
00:04:14,990 --> 00:04:16,070
But honestly,

66
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:18,519
you handled the situation today

67
00:04:18,630 --> 00:04:20,410
with such ease and composure.

68
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:23,270
If it were any other time,

69
00:04:23,270 --> 00:04:25,870
I would've chopped them up
and fed them to dogs!

70
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,100
General Li.

71
00:04:32,310 --> 00:04:33,970
General Li, please calm down.

72
00:04:34,070 --> 00:04:35,030
Calm down.

73
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,670
There's no need to be upset.

74
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:40,159
Once Shen Tongyun becomes your wife,

75
00:04:40,180 --> 00:04:41,550
when you're not happy,

76
00:04:41,580 --> 00:04:43,710
you can scold or beat her as you like,
right?

77
00:04:43,710 --> 00:04:45,790
General Li, listen to me.

78
00:04:45,850 --> 00:04:47,870
A little impatience spoils great plans.

79
00:04:47,870 --> 00:04:49,100
Once this is done,

80
00:04:49,130 --> 00:04:51,690
if you're not satisfied,

81
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:53,190
leave it to me.

82
00:04:53,220 --> 00:04:55,890
I'll find you another beautiful wife.

83
00:04:56,050 --> 00:04:57,120
What do you say?

84
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,860
Calm down, General.

85
00:04:59,740 --> 00:05:02,450
You had just left, and he already
started saying harsh words,

86
00:05:02,450 --> 00:05:04,520
talking about marrying someone else.

87
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:06,010
I'm afraid after you marry him,

88
00:05:06,010 --> 00:05:07,340
he won't treat you well.

89
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:10,100
Miss Shen, can't you see?

90
00:05:14,130 --> 00:05:14,980
Lu Chi?

91
00:05:15,510 --> 00:05:16,300
Who are you?

92
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:18,360
Why did you barge into my private room?

93
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,430
I am Lu Chi,

94
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,580
the new owner of this restaurant.

95
00:05:23,870 --> 00:05:25,730
I heard my staff member was clumsy

96
00:05:25,870 --> 00:05:27,550
and stained your robe.

97
00:05:27,750 --> 00:05:28,950
I've specially prepared
the most famous soup noodles

98
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:30,150
from the snack street

99
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:31,320
to apologize to you.

100
00:05:33,860 --> 00:05:35,320
I hope you can forgive us.

101
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:41,940
You...

102
00:05:44,310 --> 00:05:45,710
You're asking for death!

103
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:01,690
Stop!

104
00:06:06,100 --> 00:06:06,760
General Li!

105
00:06:08,640 --> 00:06:10,050
Come quickly. Hurry.

106
00:06:10,970 --> 00:06:12,640
Shen Tongyun,

107
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:14,920
are you here to die too?

108
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,520
He's way too hot-tempered.

109
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:21,920
Yes, quite frightening.

110
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:24,980
Miss Shen, you've seen it yourself.

111
00:06:25,070 --> 00:06:27,830
It's time to decide whether you want

112
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,680
to marry someone like him or not.

113
00:06:34,930 --> 00:06:37,530
General Li is talented and imposing.

114
00:06:37,630 --> 00:06:39,670
But I'm unpredictable.

115
00:06:39,700 --> 00:06:40,890
I dare not aspire to such a match.

116
00:06:40,890 --> 00:06:42,620
Let's call off our engagement.

117
00:06:43,690 --> 00:06:45,540
Everyone here can bear witness:

118
00:06:45,740 --> 00:06:47,880
I know I'm not worthy of General Li,

119
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,020
so I'm calling off the engagement.

120
00:06:49,020 --> 00:06:50,290
Don't, Miss Shen.

121
00:06:50,310 --> 00:06:51,930
Don't be deceived by Shi Fa'ke.

122
00:06:51,930 --> 00:06:54,320
This is a scheme
devised by Shi Fa'ke and Lu Chi

123
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:56,090
to frame General Li.

124
00:06:59,140 --> 00:07:01,890
Yes, I planned it.

125
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,240
But I only did this

126
00:07:03,270 --> 00:07:04,860
because someone else lied first.

127
00:07:04,860 --> 00:07:06,730
So I wanted to make him
show his true colors.

128
00:07:06,730 --> 00:07:07,550
Ms. Deng,

129
00:07:07,570 --> 00:07:09,550
you deceived Miss Shen too.

130
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:09,950
I...

131
00:07:09,950 --> 00:07:11,700
You told General Li
to pretend to be gentle

132
00:07:11,700 --> 00:07:13,170
and hide his violent nature,

133
00:07:13,170 --> 00:07:14,510
tricking Miss Shen

134
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:16,240
into marrying such a dangerous man.

135
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,440
It's marriage fraud!

136
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:18,310
You...

137
00:07:18,430 --> 00:07:19,200
Fine!

138
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:23,220
Everyone says you're fickle

139
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,460
and immoral.

140
00:07:28,130 --> 00:07:30,190
I never intended to marry you anyway!

141
00:07:31,970 --> 00:07:33,870
General Li! General Li!

142
00:07:34,950 --> 00:07:36,150
It scared me to death.

143
00:07:37,050 --> 00:07:38,730
Lu, are you alright?

144
00:07:38,830 --> 00:07:39,770
I'm fine, Ke.

145
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:40,850
Don't worry.

146
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,270
I told you, as long as I'm here,

147
00:07:42,270 --> 00:07:43,470
I promise it'll work.

148
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:47,940
Miss Shen, don't worry.

149
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:50,270
I will find you another good husband.

150
00:07:50,650 --> 00:07:52,980
I won't force fate again.

151
00:07:58,990 --> 00:07:59,790
Lu,

152
00:08:00,300 --> 00:08:02,980
Scholar Wang is right next door
at the painting shop.

153
00:08:02,980 --> 00:08:04,040
Why don't we strike while the iron is hot

154
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,500
and think of another plan?

155
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,150
Okay.

156
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,300
Don't follow me.

157
00:08:22,410 --> 00:08:23,280
[Carefree Restaurant]

158
00:08:23,280 --> 00:08:24,220
General Li!

159
00:08:25,190 --> 00:08:26,140
General Li!

160
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,240
Did you see that?

161
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:28,920
General Li!

162
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,390
That boy-crazy Shen Tongyun was leaning
over there.

163
00:08:30,390 --> 00:08:32,150
Who knows what she was looking at?

164
00:08:32,150 --> 00:08:33,890
Looking at men of course.

165
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:36,450
She was so excited
that she nearly rushed out.

166
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:39,309
Shen Tongyun is so immoral.

167
00:08:39,390 --> 00:08:40,659
Who'd dare marry a woman like her?

168
00:08:40,659 --> 00:08:41,360
[Carefree Restaurant]

169
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,960
-That's right.
-Don't slander Tongyun!

170
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,000
Who are you?

171
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,630
What business is it of yours what we say?

172
00:08:45,630 --> 00:08:47,670
What gives you the right to slander her
behind her back?

173
00:08:47,670 --> 00:08:49,390
Has she fallen in love with your sons?

174
00:08:49,390 --> 00:08:51,240
Is she going to marry into your families?

175
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,620
They are unmarried.

176
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,540
She just wants to marry a handsome man.

177
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:55,440
What's wrong with that?

178
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,170
Everyone appreciates beauty.

179
00:08:57,270 --> 00:08:58,840
She just has higher standards,

180
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,840
yet you're ruining her reputation
behind her back.

181
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:03,120
And you have the nerve
to say she's immoral?

182
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,970
What are you yelling at us for?

183
00:09:04,990 --> 00:09:06,240
She'll never get married.

184
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:08,170
No one would marry a woman like her.

185
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,600
Who says she won't?

186
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,440
Who says no one would marry her?

187
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,840
I am willing to marry her!

188
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:13,460
I'm very, very willing!

189
00:09:13,460 --> 00:09:14,500
[Carefree Restaurant]

190
00:09:14,980 --> 00:09:16,360
I'm willing to marry Shen Tongyun

191
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,970
and give her a grand wedding!

192
00:09:17,990 --> 00:09:19,720
I'll treasure her like a jewel,

193
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:22,490
loving and protecting her for a lifetime!

194
00:09:32,820 --> 00:09:36,180
[Carefree Restaurant]

195
00:09:43,030 --> 00:09:45,360
Little trinkets and charms for sale.

196
00:09:46,270 --> 00:09:47,610
Come take a look.

197
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:52,710
[Carefree Restaurant]

198
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,520
[Carefree Restaurant]

199
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:08,510
Miss Shen,

200
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:11,700
what is beauty? What is ugliness?

201
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:14,240
Isn't inner beauty the true beauty?

202
00:10:15,180 --> 00:10:16,560
Someone who truly loves you—

203
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:17,870
even if he can't have you,

204
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:19,470
he will protect you forever.

205
00:10:19,530 --> 00:10:22,580
Today, you've seen a handsome man

206
00:10:22,850 --> 00:10:24,110
but with a cruel heart.

207
00:10:24,410 --> 00:10:26,610
You should know
how precious a kind heart is.

208
00:10:26,610 --> 00:10:28,920
Beauty fades. Youth passes.

209
00:10:29,340 --> 00:10:31,270
Only someone with a beautiful soul

210
00:10:31,610 --> 00:10:33,340
can protect you for a lifetime.

211
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,500
Thank you for today, Miss Shi.

212
00:10:41,990 --> 00:10:42,850
I'm leaving.

213
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:47,830
Ke,

214
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:50,700
does Scholar Wang have no chance anymore?

215
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:53,100
You don't understand women.

216
00:10:53,390 --> 00:10:54,270
I...

217
00:10:59,140 --> 00:11:00,670
I really don't understand.

218
00:11:02,690 --> 00:11:04,530
[Yunlou Painting Shop]

219
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:14,010
Scholar Wang, congratulations.

220
00:11:14,010 --> 00:11:17,870
Tomorrow, I'll accompany you
to Shen's Mansion to propose marriage.

221
00:11:19,070 --> 00:11:19,830
Miss Shi,

222
00:11:20,570 --> 00:11:21,700
please stop joking.

223
00:11:22,740 --> 00:11:24,470
I've already given up all hope.

224
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,650
What are you talking about?

225
00:11:26,740 --> 00:11:28,740
If you give up, what about Miss Shen?

226
00:11:28,750 --> 00:11:29,840
Miss Shi,

227
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,720
Tongyun remained silent.

228
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,000
She didn't agree.

229
00:11:35,370 --> 00:11:36,710
She's a woman.

230
00:11:36,950 --> 00:11:38,850
You expect her to accept you publicly?

231
00:11:38,850 --> 00:11:41,050
Besides, you're not exactly handsome,

232
00:11:41,270 --> 00:11:43,040
yet she's still been with you for years.

233
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:44,340
And she repeatedly

234
00:11:44,630 --> 00:11:46,500
hesitated over marriage because of you.

235
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:48,740
That shows you're special to her.

236
00:11:49,170 --> 00:11:49,980
It's just that

237
00:11:50,610 --> 00:11:52,810
she can't let go of her inner obsession.

238
00:11:53,460 --> 00:11:55,340
Tomorrow, tidy yourself up,

239
00:11:55,580 --> 00:11:56,750
put on some proper clothes,

240
00:11:56,750 --> 00:11:58,190
and we'll sincerely ask for her hand.

241
00:11:58,190 --> 00:12:00,120
This marriage will surely happen.

242
00:12:08,930 --> 00:12:10,930
Thank you for your advice, Miss Shi.

243
00:12:13,980 --> 00:12:18,880
[Shen's Mansion]

244
00:12:18,880 --> 00:12:21,730
I think Miss Shen must have been moved.

245
00:12:22,370 --> 00:12:23,840
Now all that's left is...

246
00:12:24,450 --> 00:12:25,110
Miss Shi.

247
00:12:26,420 --> 00:12:27,880
Sorry to keep you waiting.

248
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:35,200
You didn't understand what I said?

249
00:12:36,090 --> 00:12:37,760
I told you to tidy yourself up,

250
00:12:37,850 --> 00:12:38,720
put on some proper clothes,

251
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,950
and sincerely ask for her hand.

252
00:12:39,950 --> 00:12:41,350
Didn't you understand?

253
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:42,870
I...

254
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:46,580
I did bathe and change my clothes.

255
00:12:47,730 --> 00:12:50,730
How is this new outfit any different
from your old one?

256
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:54,990
But it is new.

257
00:12:55,210 --> 00:12:56,670
I've never worn it before.

258
00:12:58,190 --> 00:12:59,790
Forget it, just come with me.

259
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:00,590
Come.

260
00:13:00,590 --> 00:13:01,800
[Shen's Mansion]

261
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:02,330
Hurry up.

262
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:13,970
Come in.

263
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:17,790
Master.

264
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:20,600
Master, Marquis Wu'an...

265
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:25,600
Ke is here?

266
00:13:26,630 --> 00:13:28,080
Master, you're foresighted.

267
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:30,460
Miss Shi came with Scholar Wang,

268
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:32,550
saying he's here to try on every new style

269
00:13:32,550 --> 00:13:34,540
of men's clothing in our pavilion.

270
00:13:35,150 --> 00:13:36,340
Serve them well.

271
00:13:36,510 --> 00:13:37,840
Give her whatever she asks for.

272
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:38,870
Don't neglect her.

273
00:13:38,870 --> 00:13:39,550
Yes.

274
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:40,960
Also,

275
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:43,250
don't ask her for payment.

276
00:13:43,250 --> 00:13:45,310
I understand, don't worry.

277
00:13:53,390 --> 00:13:55,140
Alright, your turn now.

278
00:13:55,390 --> 00:13:57,650
Master, you seem to value Ms. Li more.

279
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:59,080
I treat everyone equally.

280
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:00,910
Yes, you treat us equally,

281
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:02,450
but you favor Miss Shi more.

282
00:14:02,450 --> 00:14:04,250
She's always your top priority.

283
00:14:05,270 --> 00:14:06,000
Of course.

284
00:14:06,630 --> 00:14:08,360
Do you have a problem with that?

285
00:14:09,430 --> 00:14:10,160
I...

286
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:13,900
I wouldn't dare.

287
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:16,980
