for your effortless and effective idea,

294
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:30,840
saying you didn't let him down.

295
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:33,840
Also, a painting will be delivered to you
another day.

296
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:36,360
He never comes without a purpose.

297
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:40,020
If he's delivering a painting,
he must want something.

298
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:43,620
Never mind.

299
00:14:44,150 --> 00:14:45,550
I'll go check on Ke first.

300
00:14:52,250 --> 00:14:55,520
Xibao Pavilion's clothes
are truly exquisite

301
00:14:55,800 --> 00:14:57,040
and delightful.

302
00:14:59,020 --> 00:15:00,020
I understand now.

303
00:15:00,570 --> 00:15:02,490
Thank you for your advice, Miss Shi.

304
00:15:02,490 --> 00:15:04,200
For such a formal and important occasion,

305
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:06,930
