choose something more beautiful

306
00:15:07,060 --> 00:15:08,920
to show how seriously I take this.

307
00:15:09,760 --> 00:15:12,270
But I'm not good at these things.

308
00:15:12,780 --> 00:15:15,200
May I trouble you to help me pick one?

309
00:15:15,230 --> 00:15:17,490
Scholar Wang, you're truly perceptive.

310
00:15:17,580 --> 00:15:19,730
Wearing a nice outfit shows sincerity

311
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:21,350
and caters to her tastes.

312
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:22,790
Miss Shi,

313
00:15:22,870 --> 00:15:23,930
Chief said

314
00:15:23,950 --> 00:15:25,480
