315
00:15:25,480 --> 00:15:27,080
feel free to choose whatever you need.

316
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:28,960
Consider this place your own home.

317
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:30,870
No need to stand on ceremony.

318
00:15:32,270 --> 00:15:34,720
Should I forgive him or not?

319
00:15:35,510 --> 00:15:36,440
Forget it.

320
00:15:37,020 --> 00:15:40,350
I'll deal with it
after Shen Tongyun's marriage is settled.

321
00:15:40,770 --> 00:15:43,140
Scholar Wang, you have elegant demeanor.

322
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:45,230
You should choose something
in soft, muted tones,

323
00:15:45,230 --> 00:15:46,500
with some embellishments.

324
00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:48,230
And the fabric must be elegant.

325
00:15:52,230 --> 00:15:54,040
How about trying this one?

326
00:16:01,270 --> 00:16:02,000
Sounds good.

327
00:16:03,920 --> 00:16:05,580
Mr. Wang, please follow me.

328
00:16:15,420 --> 00:16:17,020
This one looks really nice.

329
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:20,680
It's sewn with gold thread.

330
00:16:21,120 --> 00:16:22,460
For Scholar Wang,

331
00:16:22,630 --> 00:16:24,290
