339
00:16:58,710 --> 00:16:59,350
Wait.

340
00:17:00,380 --> 00:17:02,920
I still feel like something's missing.

341
00:17:06,790 --> 00:17:07,760
Give me a moment.

342
00:17:13,089 --> 00:17:15,890
Miss, that's pearl powder.

343
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:17,780
