344
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:40,270
Now,

345
00:17:40,290 --> 00:17:42,740
he indeed looks better.

346
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:46,770
You are what you wear.

347
00:17:46,800 --> 00:17:48,600
The saying is absolutely right.

348
00:17:50,330 --> 00:17:51,040
Come.

349
00:18:01,470 --> 00:18:03,470
