351
00:18:07,210 --> 00:18:10,650
Then until Miss Shen is married,

352
00:18:10,910 --> 00:18:12,570
stay at least a few hundred miles away

353
00:18:12,570 --> 00:18:14,050
from Shen's Mansion,

354
00:18:14,070 --> 00:18:16,400
