355
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:18,620
A few hundred miles?

356
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:20,230
Isn't that a bit too far?

357
00:18:20,230 --> 00:18:22,430
Sorry for the inconvenience, Chief Lu.

358
00:18:23,520 --> 00:18:24,180
Let's go.

359
00:18:28,870 --> 00:18:31,160
[Shen's Mansion]

360
00:18:31,460 --> 00:18:32,970
[Information Card]

361
00:18:33,770 --> 00:18:36,380
Miss Shi, this is...

362
