363
00:18:36,460 --> 00:18:38,910
Miss Shen, take a look at Scholar Wang

364
00:18:38,980 --> 00:18:41,260
before you accept the Information Card.

365
00:18:52,270 --> 00:18:54,160
[Soothing as Gentle Wind]

366
00:18:54,160 --> 00:18:54,740
This...

367
00:18:55,760 --> 00:18:56,490
Tongyun,

368
00:18:56,780 --> 00:18:58,510
I brought you a painting today.

369
00:18:58,780 --> 00:18:59,710
Come take a look.

370
00:19:10,230 --> 00:19:11,990
This is Mr. Gushan's painting.

371
00:19:12,150 --> 00:19:14,300
Gushan Sou is an old friend of mine.

372
00:19:15,030 --> 00:19:16,410
I asked him to draw this long ago

373
00:19:16,410 --> 00:19:18,180
as a gift for your wedding.

374
00:19:19,740 --> 00:19:20,940
I just never expected

375
00:19:21,290 --> 00:19:22,690
I would have the honor...

376
00:19:24,900 --> 00:19:25,620
Tongyun,

377
00:19:27,070 --> 00:19:29,330
I specially came today to propose to you.

378
00:19:29,990 --> 00:19:30,940
If you accept me,

379
00:19:31,570 --> 00:19:34,300
I promise I'll love and protect you
for a lifetime

380
00:19:34,980 --> 00:19:36,040
and make you happy.

381
00:19:43,020 --> 00:19:44,430
And if I don't accept you,

382
00:19:44,730 --> 00:19:46,890
will you not give me this painting?

383
00:19:47,830 --> 00:19:48,670
I will.

384
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:51,690
This painting was meant
to be a gift for your wedding.

385
00:19:51,690 --> 00:19:53,020
If you agree to marry me,

386
00:19:53,100 --> 00:19:55,900
this painting will be
part of the betrothal gifts.

387
00:19:56,090 --> 00:19:56,990
If you...

388
00:19:57,500 --> 00:19:59,570
If you find another good man,

389
00:19:59,850 --> 00:20:02,980
this painting will be my gift
to celebrate your wedding.

390
00:20:04,090 --> 00:20:05,310
Miss Shen,

391
00:20:05,410 --> 00:20:07,720
Scholar Wang has loved you faithfully
for over a decade.

392
00:20:07,720 --> 00:20:08,850
He's stood the test of time.

393
00:20:08,850 --> 00:20:11,050
A good man like him should not be missed.

394
00:20:11,890 --> 00:20:13,360
The Information Card...

395
00:20:13,360 --> 00:20:14,420
[Information Card]

396
00:20:19,520 --> 00:20:21,380
Yes, I'll exchange it right away.

397
00:20:22,990 --> 00:20:24,810
Next is choosing the wedding date.

398
00:20:24,810 --> 00:20:25,890
Both families should meet

399
00:20:25,890 --> 00:20:27,090
and decide the wedding date.

400
00:20:27,090 --> 00:20:28,220
No need for all that.

401
00:20:28,290 --> 00:20:30,880
My father has long wished for me
to find a good husband.

402
00:20:30,880 --> 00:20:33,010
Today, his wish has finally come true.

403
00:20:33,850 --> 00:20:35,660
The wedding date is up to me.

404
00:20:35,870 --> 00:20:38,530
Then Miss Shen, when?

405
00:20:41,390 --> 00:20:43,570
Three days from now is an auspicious date.

406
00:20:43,570 --> 00:20:46,300
Miss Shi, please help
make all the arrangements.

407
00:20:46,310 --> 00:20:47,440
Three days from now?

408
00:20:48,430 --> 00:20:51,210
Miss Shen, isn't that a bit too soon?

409
00:20:51,230 --> 00:20:52,170
Not at all.

410
00:20:52,890 --> 00:20:55,590
Um...
I've loved Tongyun for over 10 years.

411
00:20:55,940 --> 00:20:58,200
This mustn't be delayed a moment longer.

412
00:20:58,460 --> 00:20:58,520
Please grant our wish, Miss Shi.

413
00:20:58,520 --> 00:21:00,300
[Soothing as Gentle Wind]

414
00:21:00,300 --> 00:21:02,100
