-Three days.

420
00:21:13,310 --> 00:21:13,790
How remarkably creative.

421
00:21:13,790 --> 00:21:20,540
[Shen's Mansion]

422
00:21:25,550 --> 00:21:27,460
Ke, what's wrong?

423
00:21:27,790 --> 00:21:29,130
Are you in trouble?

424
00:21:29,310 --> 00:21:30,770
Or are you feeling unwell?

425
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:33,290
Why do my clients

426
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:34,940
either refuse to marry

427
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:36,970
