428
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:38,680
Now they're even more impatient.

429
00:21:38,680 --> 00:21:40,540
They want a wedding in three days.

430
00:21:40,790 --> 00:21:42,120
What am I supposed to do?

431
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:42,930
Don't worry.

432
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:44,660
You've got me.

433
00:21:46,460 --> 00:21:48,370
You can't help me with this.

434
00:21:48,770 --> 00:21:50,250
Only Kexian can help me.

435
00:21:51,210 --> 00:21:51,980
[Shen's Mansion]

436
00:21:51,980 --> 00:21:52,800
Wait.

437
00:21:53,320 --> 00:21:54,830
I was not joking with you.

438
00:21:54,860 --> 00:21:56,460
Before Shen Tongyun gets married,

439
00:21:56,460 --> 00:21:57,230
you need to keep your distance.

440
00:21:57,230 --> 00:21:58,230
You can't show up.

441
00:21:58,640 --> 00:21:59,760
You're not keeping your distance.

442
00:21:59,760 --> 00:22:00,760
Why should I?

443
00:22:01,440 --> 00:22:03,100
What does it have to do with me?

444
00:22:03,310 --> 00:22:04,140
Remember:

445
00:22:04,350 --> 00:22:05,410
keep your distance.

446
00:22:05,410 --> 00:22:06,470
Stop following me.

447
00:22:09,970 --> 00:22:12,250
[Shen's Mansion]

448
00:22:12,920 --> 00:22:13,890
Ketian,

449
00:22:14,050 --> 00:22:15,590
if Shen Tongyun's wedding
can be held successfully,

450
00:22:15,590 --> 00:22:17,070
apart from bringing honor
to the Shi family,

451
00:22:17,070 --> 00:22:19,320
if we can prepare all the wedding cakes
within three days,

452
00:22:19,320 --> 00:22:21,350
He's Bakery will also become famous
throughout the capital.

453
00:22:21,350 --> 00:22:22,960
Don't even think about it.

454
00:22:23,030 --> 00:22:24,950
Preparing over 1,000 wedding cakes
within three days

455
00:22:24,950 --> 00:22:26,210
is simply impossible.

456
00:22:26,220 --> 00:22:28,040
Don't reject me so quickly.

457
00:22:28,070 --> 00:22:29,220
I'll pay you more.

458
00:22:29,250 --> 00:22:31,080
You can hire more people to help.
How about that?

459
00:22:31,080 --> 00:22:33,700
Kexian, please help me.

460
00:22:34,270 --> 00:22:35,650
Stop daydreaming.

461
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:37,410
-My brother...
-I'll help you.

462
00:22:38,570 --> 00:22:39,760
As long as we work day and night,

463
00:22:39,760 --> 00:22:40,960
we can finish in time.

464
00:22:42,320 --> 00:22:43,380
That's wonderful!

465
00:22:43,570 --> 00:22:44,550
I knew you two

466
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:46,750
would be the saviors of me and Miss Shen.

467
00:22:48,070 --> 00:22:50,130
Mr. He, don't push yourself too hard.

468
00:22:50,350 --> 00:22:51,950
As your younger sister said,

469
00:22:52,030 --> 00:22:53,310
making over 1,000 wedding cakes

470
00:22:53,310 --> 00:22:55,070
within three days is simply impossible.

471
00:22:55,070 --> 00:22:56,860
If I promise Ke something,

472
00:22:57,200 --> 00:22:58,800
I will make sure it gets done.

473
00:22:59,110 --> 00:23:00,380
But I wonder

474
00:23:00,440 --> 00:23:02,450
what you can do to help Ke.

475
00:23:02,550 --> 00:23:03,960
The Shen family has invited many guests.

476
00:23:03,960 --> 00:23:05,450
I'll help Ke write wedding invitations.

477
00:23:05,450 --> 00:23:07,110
So many wedding invitations—

478
00:23:07,170 --> 00:23:08,720
are you really willing
to help me write them?

479
00:23:08,720 --> 00:23:09,490
Of course.

480
00:23:09,830 --> 00:23:11,110
Have I ever lied to you?

481
00:23:16,830 --> 00:23:19,540
The three of us must work together

482
00:23:19,560 --> 00:23:20,920
to make Miss Shen's wedding

483
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:22,780
successful and grand.

484
00:23:30,760 --> 00:23:32,740
