485
00:23:36,710 --> 00:23:38,490
[Shi's Mansion]

486
00:23:39,080 --> 00:23:42,430
Wang Ren and Shen Tongyun,

487
00:23:42,830 --> 00:23:44,290
a union of destined souls.

488
00:23:44,400 --> 00:23:47,560
A perfect match, inseparable forever.

489
00:23:48,830 --> 00:23:52,270
A perfect match, inseparable forever.

490
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:55,060
With a vow to grow old together,

491
00:23:55,350 --> 00:23:57,410
pledge to establish an eternal bond.

492
00:23:58,110 --> 00:24:01,210
To grow old together,
hearts forever united.

493
00:24:01,970 --> 00:24:03,790
To grow old together,
hearts forever united.

494
00:24:03,790 --> 00:24:05,350
You're staying up all night

495
00:24:05,350 --> 00:24:07,680
just to help with someone else's wedding.

496
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:08,660
Ke,

497
00:24:09,070 --> 00:24:10,600
I promise I'll find a way

498
00:24:10,790 --> 00:24:12,720
to never let you work so hard again.

499
00:24:31,110 --> 00:24:32,290
Why are you here?

500
00:24:32,750 --> 00:24:34,340
If my two brothers see you,

501
00:24:34,680 --> 00:24:35,790
you'll get beaten again.

502
00:24:35,790 --> 00:24:37,680
I did something that deserves a beating.

503
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:38,920
If your brothers want to beat me,

504
00:24:38,920 --> 00:24:39,960
I have no choice but to accept it.

505
00:24:39,960 --> 00:24:40,590
You...

506
00:24:43,350 --> 00:24:44,520
Forget it, Lu.

507
00:24:44,960 --> 00:24:46,350
You've helped me a lot.

508
00:24:46,370 --> 00:24:47,370
You helped me

509
00:24:48,070 --> 00:24:50,530
get rid of Li Ang,
Scholar Wang's love rival.

510
00:24:51,140 --> 00:24:52,510
I should thank you for that.

511
00:24:52,510 --> 00:24:54,570
Ke, you're not angry with me anymore?

512
00:24:54,640 --> 00:24:56,170
Of course I was angry,

513
00:24:56,890 --> 00:24:58,340
but I'm over it now.

514
00:24:58,680 --> 00:25:00,940
If my brothers hadn't hurt you secretly,

515
00:25:01,030 --> 00:25:02,310
you wouldn't have had the chance
to fake illness.

516
00:25:02,310 --> 00:25:02,950
Anyway,

517
00:25:03,830 --> 00:25:05,100
it's their fault.

518
00:25:05,200 --> 00:25:05,740
Ke,

519
00:25:06,790 --> 00:25:07,370
I...

520
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:08,020
Lu,

521
00:25:09,050 --> 00:25:10,980
have you forgotten why I was angry?

522
00:25:11,370 --> 00:25:12,810
Mind your manners.

523
00:25:18,480 --> 00:25:19,920
Don't think about it.

524
00:25:19,960 --> 00:25:22,020
Shi Fa'ke, you're engaged.

525
00:25:22,440 --> 00:25:25,170
How can you lose your composure
over another man?

526
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:28,260
I'll leave the invitations here.

527
00:25:28,310 --> 00:25:29,910
Don't forget to pick them up.

528
00:25:35,400 --> 00:25:36,110
Get down!

529
00:25:37,610 --> 00:25:39,170
Chief Lu, no more pretense?

530
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:40,330
Xianxian, beat him!

531
00:25:41,790 --> 00:25:42,540
Stop!

532
00:25:43,790 --> 00:25:45,620
Xianxian, Chongshan, what are you doing?

533
00:25:45,620 --> 00:25:47,110
Lu has regained his memory.

534
00:25:47,110 --> 00:25:47,880
He's well now.

535
00:25:47,880 --> 00:25:49,690
Ke, he was pretending.

536
00:25:49,710 --> 00:25:51,570
