543
00:26:03,200 --> 00:26:04,930
Chongshan, I'm suddenly sleepy.

544
00:26:04,930 --> 00:26:05,990
Help me back to bed.

545
00:26:06,110 --> 00:26:07,070
Mr. Lu is afraid of the dark.

546
00:26:07,070 --> 00:26:07,790
Let's go together.

547
00:26:07,790 --> 00:26:09,200
I'm not afraid of the dark.

548
00:26:09,200 --> 00:26:09,960
Wait.

549
00:26:10,350 --> 00:26:13,050
I said Lu must not be harmed.

550
00:26:13,310 --> 00:26:13,850
Your hands.

551
00:26:13,850 --> 00:26:14,910
Remove your hands.

552
00:26:18,220 --> 00:26:19,880
Lu, come here.

553
00:26:23,330 --> 00:26:24,730
This is a secret.

554
00:26:24,750 --> 00:26:26,410
Don't let them find out.

555
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:32,150
