561
00:27:21,650 --> 00:27:23,290
and fulfilled the wishes of your parents.

562
00:27:23,290 --> 00:27:25,180
Today, you are joined in marriage.

563
00:27:25,180 --> 00:27:26,290
The ceremony is complete!

564
00:27:26,290 --> 00:27:27,170
Congratulations.

565
00:27:27,170 --> 00:27:28,030
Congratulations.

566
00:27:28,030 --> 00:27:29,070
A perfect match of talent and beauty.

567
00:27:29,070 --> 00:27:29,440
Indeed.

568
00:27:29,440 --> 00:27:30,790
Congratulations.

569
00:27:31,720 --> 00:27:32,830
Congratulations.

570
00:27:32,830 --> 00:27:33,900
Such a lovely couple.

571
00:27:33,900 --> 00:27:35,300
Truly a perfect match.

572
00:27:36,230 --> 00:27:38,360
They truly are perfect for each other.

573
00:27:40,270 --> 00:27:42,000
Tongyun lost her mother early,

574
00:27:42,640 --> 00:27:44,500
so I took on the role of her mother.

575
00:27:44,640 --> 00:27:46,880
I've always worried
I haven't taken care of her well enough,

576
00:27:46,880 --> 00:27:48,420
so I've spoiled her a bit.

577
00:27:49,030 --> 00:27:51,810
Now that someone truly cares about her,

578
00:27:52,270 --> 00:27:53,790
I can finally be at ease.

579
00:27:53,830 --> 00:27:55,300
Father-in-law, rest assured.

580
00:27:55,300 --> 00:27:56,700
I will treat Tongyun well

581
00:27:57,040 --> 00:27:58,100
and make her happy.

582
00:27:58,550 --> 00:27:59,250
Good.

583
00:28:00,310 --> 00:28:00,940
Good.

584
00:28:01,920 --> 00:28:02,890
Very good.

585
00:28:03,640 --> 00:28:04,750
Miss Shi.

586
00:28:05,220 --> 00:28:07,640
Lord Shen, what are you doing?

587
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:09,110
You'll overwhelm me with such courtesy.

588
00:28:09,110 --> 00:28:11,610
Miss Shi, this honor is well deserved.

589
00:28:12,270 --> 00:28:14,030
It was your mother, Tao,

590
00:28:14,030 --> 00:28:16,640
who arranged the marriage
between Tongyun's mother and me.

591
00:28:16,640 --> 00:28:19,760
And now, you've found
such a good husband for Tongyun.

592
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:22,380
I'm very grateful.

593
00:28:22,550 --> 00:28:25,420
The No.1 matchmaker in the world

594
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:27,480
clearly has a worthy successor.

595
00:28:27,790 --> 00:28:29,170
It was my duty.

596
00:28:29,270 --> 00:28:30,730
Lord Shen, you flatter me.

597
00:28:30,880 --> 00:28:33,120
They have finally become husband and wife.

598
00:28:33,120 --> 00:28:34,380
I'm happy for them too.

599
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:35,880
Well said.

600
00:28:37,440 --> 00:28:38,030
Ke.

601
00:28:40,060 --> 00:28:43,420
♪ Fate is holding the thread in my hand ♪

602
00:28:43,420 --> 00:28:44,110
Let's go.

603
00:28:46,230 --> 00:28:47,090
♪ If you appear in dreams once again ♪

604
00:28:47,090 --> 00:28:47,890
Ren.

605
00:28:51,830 --> 00:28:53,380
♪ I am willing to be led by you ♪

606
00:28:53,380 --> 00:28:54,070
Miss Shi.

607
00:28:54,200 --> 00:28:56,150
Miss Shen, what is it?

608
00:28:56,790 --> 00:28:57,150
Don't miss the auspicious hour
for consummating your marriage.

609
00:28:57,150 --> 00:29:01,430
♪ My heart will never change ♪

610
00:29:02,120 --> 00:29:03,140
Miss Shi, don't worry.

611
00:29:03,140 --> 00:29:04,450
♪ Can't untangle it,
yet I sink into longing ♪

612
00:29:04,450 --> 00:29:06,180
I'm not going to change my mind.

613
00:29:06,360 --> 00:29:08,870
It's just on this joyous day,
my heart is tinged with emotion.

614
00:29:08,870 --> 00:29:09,680
♪ Can't tell if it's bitter or sweet ♪

615
00:29:09,680 --> 00:29:11,880
In the past, I was infatuated
with handsome men.

616
00:29:11,880 --> 00:29:13,130
I was wrong.

617
00:29:13,820 --> 00:29:15,980
Today, I finally understand true affection
weighs far more than outward beauty.

618
00:29:15,980 --> 00:29:17,500
♪ For a lifetime ♪

619
00:29:18,120 --> 00:29:18,500
I will grow old with Ren

620
00:29:18,500 --> 00:29:20,250
♪ A bond of hearts ♪

621
00:29:21,030 --> 00:29:21,420
to repay your kindness.

622
00:29:21,420 --> 00:29:22,120
♪ Tying a bond of earthly joy,
where love blooms and the moon is full ♪

623
00:29:22,120 --> 00:29:23,880
I should thank you.

624
00:29:24,720 --> 00:29:26,440
You've found understanding through love,

625
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:27,990
while I've found mine through action.

626
00:29:27,990 --> 00:29:28,050
♪ The poem continues
in rich ink and flowing script ♪

627
00:29:28,050 --> 00:29:29,810
You repay me with lifelong devotion,

628
00:29:29,810 --> 00:29:31,940
and I repay my clients with sincerity.

629
00:29:33,920 --> 00:29:37,710
♪ Even zithers
stir the strings of the heart ♪

630
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:39,120
Mother, I understand you now.

631
00:29:39,120 --> 00:29:41,200
♪ Silken threads of love,
feelings intertwined ♪

632
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:42,920
A matchmaker's work is not for fame,

633
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:43,150
♪ Forming a bond of hearts ♪

634
00:29:43,150 --> 00:29:44,150
nor for fortune,

635
00:29:44,680 --> 00:29:45,760
but simply to help clients find the one

636
00:29:45,760 --> 00:29:46,570
♪ Hold our hands ♪

637
00:29:46,650 --> 00:29:47,160
with whom to grow old together.

638
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:48,050
♪ Not letting go ♪

639
00:29:48,940 --> 00:29:50,420
♪ Forever ♪

640
00:29:50,420 --> 00:29:52,200
That deep sense of honor
born from the heart

641
00:29:52,200 --> 00:29:53,440
♪ Let spring breeze ease my longing ♪

642
00:29:53,440 --> 00:29:54,840
is what I should protect.

643
00:29:55,650 --> 00:29:56,940
♪ I'd trade immortality
to see you each year ♪

644
00:29:56,940 --> 00:29:58,480
And that's the essence
of being the No.1 matchmaker in the world.

645
00:29:58,480 --> 00:30:01,620
♪ Hand in hand,
we watch the stars unfold ♪

646
00:30:02,780 --> 00:30:02,790
♪ Silken threads of love,
feelings intertwined ♪

647
00:30:02,790 --> 00:30:03,480
Ke,

648
00:30:04,420 --> 00:30:06,350
I will also hold fast to my feelings

649
00:30:06,390 --> 00:30:07,020
and stay by your side.

650
00:30:07,020 --> 00:30:08,700
♪ Forming a bond of hearts ♪

651
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:09,290
I only hope that one day,

652
00:30:09,290 --> 00:30:10,330
♪ Even if mulberry fields ♪

653
00:30:10,910 --> 00:30:11,460
♪ Turn to seas ♪

654
00:30:11,460 --> 00:30:12,590
I can also get what I've longed for.

655
00:30:12,590 --> 00:30:16,430
♪ My heart will never change ♪

656
00:30:27,440 --> 00:30:28,580
Come on.

657
00:30:32,810 --> 00:30:34,190
Miss Shi!

658
00:30:34,310 --> 00:30:35,470
Miss Shi!

659
00:30:35,790 --> 00:30:37,010
Where is Miss Shi?

660
00:30:38,580 --> 00:30:39,000
Be careful.

661
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:40,020
Miss Shi!

662
00:30:40,110 --> 00:30:41,870
Where are you, Miss Shi?

663
00:30:43,550 --> 00:30:47,610
On behalf of my niece,
I offer you this toast. Please drink it!

664
00:30:49,030 --> 00:30:49,970
Miss Shi!

665
00:30:50,070 --> 00:30:51,880
Don't stop me. I can drink more.

666
00:31:05,860 --> 00:31:08,620
Lu, what are you doing?

667
00:31:09,310 --> 00:31:11,500
I know your alcohol tolerance very well.

668
00:31:11,500 --> 00:31:13,300
You get drunk after just one cup.

669
00:31:13,540 --> 00:31:14,150
Wait.

670
00:31:15,170 --> 00:31:17,100
Why does this scene feel so familiar?

671
00:31:17,100 --> 00:31:18,900
If you can't remember, maybe...

672
00:31:19,160 --> 00:31:19,800
Right!

673
00:31:20,930 --> 00:31:22,080
I remember now.

674
00:31:22,110 --> 00:31:23,730
I promised to do a few things for you,

675
00:31:23,730 --> 00:31:25,010
and I haven't fulfilled them yet.

676
00:31:25,010 --> 00:31:26,840
Whether I've forgiven you or not,

677
00:31:26,840 --> 00:31:28,400
I will keep my word.

678
00:31:33,310 --> 00:31:35,450
I'd like to put
what you promised me on hold.

679
00:31:35,450 --> 00:31:37,780
I'll tell you
once I figure out what I want.

680
00:31:37,830 --> 00:31:38,580
But Ke,

681
00:31:39,180 --> 00:31:41,380
what must I do to earn your forgiveness?

682
00:31:42,410 --> 00:31:43,940
You haven't figured it out,

683
00:31:44,030 --> 00:31:45,060
but I have.

684
00:31:46,070 --> 00:31:47,120
What do you want?

685
00:31:47,190 --> 00:31:49,550
Buy me street snacks for a month.

686
00:31:49,570 --> 00:31:50,350
No repeats allowed.

687
00:31:50,350 --> 00:31:51,610
Then I'll forgive you.

688
00:31:52,830 --> 00:31:53,660
It's a deal.

689
00:31:54,920 --> 00:31:55,760
Deal.

690
00:32:01,440 --> 00:32:03,450
Ke, you're breaking propriety again.

691
00:32:03,450 --> 00:32:05,650
I'm worried you'll go back on your word.

692
00:32:06,260 --> 00:32:07,370
I never will.

693
00:32:07,550 --> 00:32:10,810
Starting tomorrow,
I'll be waiting at your door every day.

694
00:32:11,720 --> 00:32:12,270
Okay.

695
00:32:23,270 --> 00:32:23,640
You're asking for death!

696
00:32:23,640 --> 00:32:24,550
My Lord, spare me!

697
00:32:24,550 --> 00:32:25,550
Please spare my life!

698
00:32:25,550 --> 00:32:28,440
I'll send someone right now
to wipe out the entire Shen family!

699
00:32:28,440 --> 00:32:30,960
No matter what it takes,
I'll find that construction drawing.

700
00:32:30,960 --> 00:32:32,160
If I can't find it,

701
00:32:32,310 --> 00:32:33,830
I'll just burn everything to the ground

702
00:32:33,830 --> 00:32:34,610
and end it.

703
00:32:34,640 --> 00:32:36,380
After the killing and burning, then what?

704
00:32:36,380 --> 00:32:36,920
Then...

705
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:39,770
Then word reaches His Majesty,

706
00:32:39,960 --> 00:32:41,000
and he starts investigating me?

707
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:42,460
Or do you want to remind him

708
00:32:42,550 --> 00:32:45,790
that I'm after the drawing
to usurp the throne?

709
00:32:46,030 --> 00:32:47,620
I'm foolish.

710
00:32:47,790 --> 00:32:48,700
I just want

711
00:32:48,730 --> 00:32:50,510
to eliminate those who disobey you.

712
00:32:50,510 --> 00:32:52,990
You're an absolute idiot!

713
00:32:53,920 --> 00:32:56,280
Now what happened
between Li Ang and Shen Tongyun

714
00:32:56,280 --> 00:32:57,560
is known to everyone.

715
00:32:57,790 --> 00:32:59,950
If you kill and burn at this moment,

716
00:33:00,070 --> 00:33:02,110
it's the same as announcing to the world

717
00:33:02,110 --> 00:33:03,920
that Li Ang and I are behind it.

718
00:33:04,810 --> 00:33:08,080
We haven't obtained
the construction drawing,

719
00:33:08,640 --> 00:33:12,580
but as long as I get the position

720
00:33:12,680 --> 00:33:14,440
of the Commander
of the Imperial Cavalry Bureau,

721
00:33:14,440 --> 00:33:17,230
it'll be easy for me

722
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:20,860
to enter the capital.

723
00:33:21,310 --> 00:33:24,060
My Lord, you truly are wise

724
00:33:24,310 --> 00:33:25,820
and resourceful.

725
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:28,870
Will General Li Ang
take on this important role?

726
00:33:29,270 --> 00:33:30,270
Idiot.

727
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:32,180
His Majesty already knows

728
00:33:32,310 --> 00:33:33,790
about his temper and character.

729
00:33:33,790 --> 00:33:37,030
His reputation has been ruined.
How could it possibly be him?

730
00:33:37,030 --> 00:33:37,550
Get up.

731
00:33:40,680 --> 00:33:41,790
Wait and see.

732
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:45,560
Whoever gets the position will be my man.

733
00:33:46,270 --> 00:33:47,640
Then I'll have
the Official Matchmaking Agency

734
00:33:47,640 --> 00:33:49,800
arrange a proper marriage for him.

735
00:33:50,030 --> 00:33:53,200
I'll have him completely under my thumb.

736
00:33:53,270 --> 00:33:54,990
[Shi's Ancestral Hall]

737
00:33:55,110 --> 00:33:57,770
[No.1 Matchmaker in the World]

738
00:34:09,030 --> 00:34:10,239
Ancestors,

739
00:34:10,270 --> 00:34:11,800
I have not disgraced our family.

740
00:34:11,800 --> 00:34:14,080
I've secured a good marriage
for Miss Shen.

741
00:34:14,080 --> 00:34:16,659
Today, they have become husband and wife.

742
00:34:19,630 --> 00:34:21,510
Ke, you're back.

743
00:34:24,150 --> 00:34:25,020
Mother.

744
00:34:26,560 --> 00:34:27,960
You drank alcohol again?

745
00:34:27,980 --> 00:34:30,840
Mother, I was smarter this time.

746
00:34:30,980 --> 00:34:33,340
When they offered me wine, I hid away.

747
00:34:33,550 --> 00:34:35,710
You're not blaming me
for coming back late, are you?

748
00:34:35,710 --> 00:34:36,900
I came back after the wedding was over

749
00:34:36,900 --> 00:34:38,630
and the guests had all left.

750
00:34:38,659 --> 00:34:40,409
I know you're thoughtful.

751
00:34:40,550 --> 00:34:41,800
I won't blame you.

752
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:44,050
I knew you love me the most.

753
00:34:44,070 --> 00:34:45,820
Thanks to our ancestors' blessing,

754
00:34:45,820 --> 00:34:48,800
Mother, I successfully arranged
Shen Tongyun's marriage.

755
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:49,630
Are you happy?

756
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:51,400
Of course I'm happy.

757
00:34:52,510 --> 00:34:53,520
Silly girl,

758
00:34:53,670 --> 00:34:56,270
the ancestors don't have time
for such things.

759
00:34:56,550 --> 00:34:58,320
It was all because of your own hard work

760
00:34:58,320 --> 00:34:59,980
that this good match was made.

761
00:35:00,030 --> 00:35:01,210
You did very well.

762
00:35:01,440 --> 00:35:03,010
I'm proud of you.

763
00:35:05,540 --> 00:35:07,410
Ancestors, did you hear that?

764
00:35:07,840 --> 00:35:09,040
My mother praised me.

765
00:35:09,710 --> 00:35:10,700
You silly girl.

766
00:35:11,550 --> 00:35:12,540
Mother.

767
00:35:12,630 --> 00:35:14,830
I don't know if the ancestors helped me,

768
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:16,320
but our neighbor, Lu,

769
00:35:16,370 --> 00:35:17,550
helped me a lot.

770
00:35:18,070 --> 00:35:19,590
Although last time, he...

771
00:35:20,670 --> 00:35:21,560
Father and my brothers bullied him first.

772
00:35:21,560 --> 00:35:23,310
[Etiquette and Morality]

773
00:35:23,710 --> 00:35:24,770
I know.

774
00:35:25,190 --> 00:35:27,750
Your father and brothers

775
00:35:27,770 --> 00:35:28,900
did go too far.

776
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:31,120
Since he helped you,

777
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:33,550
you should properly thank him.

778
00:35:34,030 --> 00:35:35,500
Mother, I will.

779
00:35:35,630 --> 00:35:37,140
Ke, promise me

780
00:35:37,280 --> 00:35:38,880
to be a good marriage broker.

781
00:35:39,030 --> 00:35:40,250
Always remember

782
00:35:40,320 --> 00:35:42,800
the words I often told you.

783
00:35:42,880 --> 00:35:44,620
Mother, don't worry.

784
00:35:45,110 --> 00:35:47,630
Be an honest matchmaker
and achieve matchmaking with honesty.

785
00:35:47,630 --> 00:35:48,630
I remember that.

786
00:35:49,480 --> 00:35:51,320
You truly are my good daughter.

787
00:35:59,010 --> 00:36:01,440
Wait, Lu Chi helped arrange

788
00:36:01,550 --> 00:36:03,210
Shen Tongyun's marriage too?

789
00:36:03,510 --> 00:36:05,080
And Ke has made up with him?

790
00:36:05,110 --> 00:36:06,130
Most importantly,

791
00:36:06,130 --> 00:36:07,610
Mother said we should thank him.

792
00:36:07,610 --> 00:36:09,480
Father, what should we do now?

793
00:36:11,950 --> 00:36:13,840
I don't understand this.

794
00:36:15,110 --> 00:36:16,840
Anyway, your mother has already agreed.

795
00:36:16,840 --> 00:36:19,210
We can't make her unhappy, right?

796
00:36:19,320 --> 00:36:20,550
But remember this—

797
00:36:21,110 --> 00:36:22,770
Ke is the apple of our eye.

798
00:36:22,960 --> 00:36:25,090
We must not let anyone take her from us.

799
00:36:25,090 --> 00:36:25,800
Exactly.

800
00:36:26,070 --> 00:36:27,200
Now listen, you two.

801
00:36:27,230 --> 00:36:28,860
Keep an eye on her every day.

802
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:30,670
Be wary of Lu Chi.

803
00:36:30,700 --> 00:36:32,150
Okay. Me first.

804
00:36:32,440 --> 00:36:33,620
I patrol the streets every day.

805
00:36:33,620 --> 00:36:35,020
It's convenient for me to follow them.

806
00:36:35,020 --> 00:36:35,820
When I'm busy,

807
00:36:35,890 --> 00:36:37,150
Chongshan, you're up.

808
00:36:37,440 --> 00:36:37,840
Okay.

809
00:36:38,030 --> 00:36:39,460
Come on, for Ke's sake.

810
00:36:42,570 --> 00:36:43,170
Father.

811
00:36:43,570 --> 00:36:45,370
Why did you use so much strength?

812
00:36:47,570 --> 00:36:48,550
[Ping'an Alley]

813
00:36:48,550 --> 00:36:49,480
You're saying...

814
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:50,050
this morning,

815
00:36:50,050 --> 00:36:52,260
when you were waiting for me
outside my house,

816
00:36:52,260 --> 00:36:54,210
my father and brothers
didn't give you any trouble,

817
00:36:54,210 --> 00:36:55,820
and they were very nice to you?

818
00:36:55,820 --> 00:36:57,160
Not exactly nice.

819
00:36:57,320 --> 00:36:59,110
They just ignored me and left.

820
00:36:59,140 --> 00:37:00,260
You don't understand.

821
00:37:00,260 --> 00:37:01,790
You tricked them last time.

822
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:04,630
They were being nice enough
that they didn't drive you away.

823
00:37:04,630 --> 00:37:06,060
I guess you're right.

824
00:37:06,710 --> 00:37:07,830
I hope

825
00:37:07,920 --> 00:37:09,810
they can continue to be nice.

826
00:37:09,840 --> 00:37:11,720
Then my month-long snack plan

827
00:37:11,740 --> 00:37:13,540
won't be interrupted by anyone.

828
00:37:14,660 --> 00:37:15,800
[Jiang's Restaurant]

829
00:37:23,090 --> 00:37:23,970
Ke!

830
00:37:25,030 --> 00:37:25,840
Ke!

831
00:37:27,310 --> 00:37:29,090
Ke, where are you going?

832
00:37:29,200 --> 00:37:30,280
I'll go with you.

833
00:37:31,360 --> 00:37:34,010
Xianxian, aren't you on patrol?

834
00:37:34,030 --> 00:37:34,950
It doesn't matter.

835
00:37:34,950 --> 00:37:37,070
I can patrol the streets
and accompany you at the same time.

836
00:37:37,070 --> 00:37:38,880
You guys, go check over there.

837
00:37:39,150 --> 00:37:40,000
-Yes.
-Yes.

838
00:37:41,030 --> 00:37:43,000
Well then, Ke, Shi,

839
00:37:43,230 --> 00:37:43,920
let's go together.

840
00:37:43,920 --> 00:37:44,470
Okay.

841
00:37:45,280 --> 00:37:45,840
Let's go.

842
00:37:47,710 --> 00:37:48,820
[Fried Cherries]

843
00:37:54,400 --> 00:37:55,730
Sir, give me one skewer.

844
00:37:56,190 --> 00:37:57,230
Okay. They're freshly grilled.

845
00:37:57,230 --> 00:37:57,960
Thanks.

846
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:06,210
One more skewer.

847
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:07,940
Here you go.

848
00:38:17,070 --> 00:38:18,000
One more skewer.

849
00:38:25,630 --> 00:38:26,690
Delicious, right?

850
00:39:01,650 --> 00:39:03,630
[Shi's Pawnshop]

851
00:39:03,630 --> 00:39:04,630
Miss Shi.

852
00:39:04,630 --> 00:39:06,590
Wang Ren, Miss Shen.

853
00:39:08,980 --> 00:39:10,170
Officer.

854
00:39:10,190 --> 00:39:11,740
Look, this is my husband.

855
00:39:11,760 --> 00:39:13,030
Isn't he handsome and dashing,

856
00:39:13,030 --> 00:39:14,290
with extraordinary demeanor?

857
00:39:14,290 --> 00:39:16,000
He is indeed good-looking.

858
00:39:16,120 --> 00:39:17,090
Let go. Let go.

859
00:39:17,250 --> 00:39:19,380
Wifey, keep a low profile.

860
00:39:19,410 --> 00:39:21,310
I'm not handsome or dashing.

861
00:39:21,330 --> 00:39:22,360
I have no extraordinary demeanor either.

862
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:23,280
Yes, you are.

863
00:39:23,300 --> 00:39:24,480
You are handsome and dashing,

864
00:39:24,480 --> 00:39:26,210
with extraordinary demeanor.

865
00:39:26,450 --> 00:39:28,330
Officer, am I wrong?

866
00:39:28,360 --> 00:39:29,150
Am I right?

867
00:39:29,150 --> 00:39:30,480
Well, let go. Let go.

868
00:39:30,480 --> 00:39:32,810
Men and women should keep their distance.

869
00:39:33,480 --> 00:39:34,500
Listen,

870
00:39:34,670 --> 00:39:36,330
control yourselves a bit.

871
00:39:36,550 --> 00:39:38,320
If you keep harassing passersby like this,

872
00:39:38,320 --> 00:39:40,650
I'll take you to the magistrate's office.

873
00:39:41,760 --> 00:39:42,360
Xianxian.

874
00:39:43,430 --> 00:39:44,310
Goodbye.

875
00:39:49,100 --> 00:39:50,560
Why are you laughing?

876
00:39:50,960 --> 00:39:53,400
I told you Miss Shen is straightforward.

877
00:39:53,430 --> 00:39:55,310
She was just speaking her mind.

878
00:39:55,330 --> 00:39:56,440
What's wrong with admiring beauty?

879
00:39:56,440 --> 00:39:57,360
You're right,

880
00:39:57,550 --> 00:39:58,800
but I wasn't laughing at her.

881
00:39:58,800 --> 00:40:00,530
Everyone appreciates beauty.

882
00:40:00,850 --> 00:40:02,100
I was just surprised—

883
00:40:02,230 --> 00:40:03,800
your eldest brother looks tough,

884
00:40:03,800 --> 00:40:05,400
yet he's terrified of women.

885
00:40:05,480 --> 00:40:06,410
What did you say?

886
00:40:07,920 --> 00:40:10,350
I said now that Shi has left,

887
00:40:10,480 --> 00:40:12,080
we can go enjoy soup noodles properly.

888
00:40:12,080 --> 00:40:12,990
What are we waiting for?

889
00:40:12,990 --> 00:40:14,200
Let's go now.

890
00:40:19,680 --> 00:40:20,630
Come on.

891
00:40:24,290 --> 00:40:26,510
[Xibao Pavilion]

892
00:40:30,000 --> 00:40:31,280
Flower House.

893
00:40:32,590 --> 00:40:34,450
Looks like I need to go take a look.

894
00:40:35,190 --> 00:40:38,030
The performances at Flower House
are quite spectacular.

895
00:40:38,030 --> 00:40:40,200
Especially Ms. Hua, the owner,

896
00:40:40,280 --> 00:40:42,210
who is said to be a peerless beauty.

897
00:40:44,230 --> 00:40:45,490
Indeed, she's pretty.

898
00:40:46,060 --> 00:40:47,300
Master,

899
00:40:47,440 --> 00:40:49,480
can you take me

900
00:40:49,510 --> 00:40:51,710
to Flower House to broaden my horizons?

901
00:40:51,920 --> 00:40:54,630
I have something important
to discuss with Ms. Li.

902
00:40:54,630 --> 00:40:57,360
Master, you want to take Ms. Li there?

903
00:40:59,230 --> 00:41:00,640
I'll take Ke with me.

904
00:41:01,480 --> 00:41:02,280
You may leave.

905
00:41:07,510 --> 00:41:09,840
Master, these are this month's accounts.

906
00:41:09,860 --> 00:41:11,190
Please take a look.

907
00:41:17,440 --> 00:41:18,400
These days,

908
00:41:18,480 --> 00:41:20,760
Shi Xianxian has been following me and Ke.

909
00:41:20,760 --> 00:41:22,560
It's been rather inconvenient.

910
00:41:27,800 --> 00:41:30,370
I heard he's terrified of women
getting too close.

911
00:41:30,370 --> 00:41:32,770
I guess you have ways
to get him away from us.

912
00:41:36,280 --> 00:41:37,860
Yes, I understand.

913
00:41:45,300 --> 00:41:48,320
[Flower House]

914
00:41:48,320 --> 00:41:50,120
This young lady is so beautiful.

915
00:41:53,430 --> 00:41:56,060
Lu, what is this place?

916
00:41:56,080 --> 00:41:58,000
This doesn't look like a place for food.

917
00:41:58,000 --> 00:41:59,600
It's got more than good food.

918
00:41:59,630 --> 00:42:01,280
There are also wonderful performances.

919
00:42:01,280 --> 00:42:01,920
Follow me.

920
00:42:07,530 --> 00:42:07,630
[Flower House]

921
00:42:07,630 --> 00:42:08,920
Take a look!

922
00:42:09,030 --> 00:42:09,710
Take a look!

923
00:42:09,710 --> 00:42:10,590
Young Master, anything you need?

924
00:42:10,590 --> 00:42:13,030
[Revelry of Peace]

925
00:42:15,270 --> 00:42:18,580
[Hua Yuerong,
the top courtesan at Flower House]

926
00:42:26,070 --> 00:42:26,800
Impressive.

927
00:42:31,190 --> 00:42:33,730
-Wonderful!
-Impressive!

928
00:42:34,480 --> 00:42:35,280
So beautiful.

929
00:42:35,280 --> 00:42:36,000
The second one is beautiful too.

930
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:36,570
Yes.

931
00:42:37,470 --> 00:42:38,630
[Revelry of Peace]

932
00:42:38,630 --> 00:42:40,050
Indeed.

933
00:42:47,510 --> 00:42:49,450
[Revelry of Peace]

934
00:42:49,450 --> 00:42:50,940
Truly beautiful.

935
00:42:52,830 --> 00:42:54,690
It's not just her looks—

936
00:42:55,150 --> 00:42:56,530
her dancing is so captivating too.

937
00:42:56,530 --> 00:42:57,320
Yes.

938
00:42:57,340 --> 00:42:57,800
Really impressive.

939
00:42:57,800 --> 00:43:01,190
Lu, do you think this dancer is beautiful?

940
00:43:03,150 --> 00:43:04,080
Come on. Cheers.

941
00:43:05,710 --> 00:43:07,110
She is indeed beautiful.

942
00:43:11,780 --> 00:43:13,490
Men are so shallow.

943
00:43:13,690 --> 00:43:15,890
You're only attracted to pretty women.

944
00:43:17,510 --> 00:43:20,350
Actually, I was just teasing you.

945
00:43:21,000 --> 00:43:23,360
Her smile isn't as captivating as yours,

946
00:43:23,630 --> 00:43:26,450
and there's no true emotion in her dance.

947
00:43:27,540 --> 00:43:28,900
That's more like it.

948
00:43:31,010 --> 00:43:32,610
These grapes are very sweet.

949
00:43:33,430 --> 00:43:34,680
Have you heard?

950
00:43:34,680 --> 00:43:34,760
[Revelry of Peace]

951
00:43:34,760 --> 00:43:36,840
These days, nobles and high officials

952
00:43:36,840 --> 00:43:38,480
have been flocking to Hua Yuerong's shows.

953
00:43:38,480 --> 00:43:40,890
That's why all the evening shows
have been canceled.

954
00:43:40,890 --> 00:43:43,160
We can only see her in the daytime.

955
00:43:43,840 --> 00:43:44,920
That's right.

956
00:43:45,000 --> 00:43:47,260
Especially Vice Commander Xu Ao.

957
00:43:47,440 --> 00:43:49,270
I've seen him come a few times.

958
00:43:49,400 --> 00:43:51,630
He always went
to the private room upstairs.

959
00:43:51,630 --> 00:43:54,080
There must be something between them.

960
00:43:54,320 --> 00:43:55,800
He's young and accomplished.

961
00:43:55,800 --> 00:43:57,700
He is now at the peak of his career.

962
00:43:57,960 --> 00:43:59,760
Of course he's in a good mood.

963
00:43:59,760 --> 00:44:00,670
A man

964
00:44:01,030 --> 00:44:02,680
unwinds a little at night—

965
00:44:02,920 --> 00:44:04,520
nothing strange about that.

966
00:44:05,480 --> 00:44:07,140
That makes sense.

967
00:44:08,070 --> 00:44:09,330
Here, a toast to you.

968
00:44:14,130 --> 00:44:15,800
Lu, let's go.

969
00:44:16,070 --> 00:44:17,870
Don't listen to their nonsense.

970
00:44:20,480 --> 00:44:22,120
She really is a great dancer.

971
00:44:27,710 --> 00:44:28,510
Ke,

972
00:44:29,230 --> 00:44:30,000
why are you angry?

973
00:44:30,000 --> 00:44:31,110
Candied haws.

974
00:44:31,400 --> 00:44:34,030
I just hate hearing people slander others
behind their backs.

975
00:44:34,030 --> 00:44:35,710
I know that Xu Ao they were talking about.

976
00:44:35,710 --> 00:44:37,460
My mother was the one
who arranged his marriage.

977
00:44:37,460 --> 00:44:38,960
Though he has a humble background,

978
00:44:38,960 --> 00:44:40,030
he is an upright person.

979
00:44:40,030 --> 00:44:41,800
It is impossible to judge a man's heart
from his face.

980
00:44:41,800 --> 00:44:43,010
It's been so long.

981
00:44:43,150 --> 00:44:44,880
Perhaps he has really changed.

982
00:44:45,340 --> 00:44:46,400
Impossible.

983
00:44:46,760 --> 00:44:48,630
My mother has met all kinds of people.
Her judgment is impeccable.

984
00:44:48,630 --> 00:44:50,190
She wouldn't be wrong about him.

985
00:44:50,190 --> 00:44:53,120
Yes, Ms. Tao's eye for character
is unmatched.

986
00:44:53,280 --> 00:44:55,620
Ke, don't bother with those people.

987
00:44:55,760 --> 00:44:58,070
My mother was
the No.1 matchmaker in the world.

988
00:44:58,070 --> 00:44:59,070
Everyone knows

989
00:44:59,070 --> 00:45:00,820
the marriages she arranged
are all good ones.

990
00:45:00,820 --> 00:45:02,150
They're all perfect matches.

991
00:45:02,150 --> 00:45:04,780
By His Majesty's order, we're on our way
to deliver an imperial edict!

992
00:45:04,780 --> 00:45:07,510
Vice Commander of the Imperial Cavalry,
Xu Ao, has been promoted!

993
00:45:07,510 --> 00:45:09,700
All unrelated persons, out of the way!

994
00:45:09,800 --> 00:45:12,670
By His Majesty's order, we're on our way
to deliver an imperial edict!

995
00:45:12,670 --> 00:45:15,510
Vice Commander of the Imperial Cavalry,
Xu Ao, has been promoted!

996
00:45:15,510 --> 00:45:17,640
All unrelated persons, out of the way!

997
00:45:18,850 --> 00:45:19,760
What did I tell you?

998
00:45:19,760 --> 00:45:21,510
Xu Ao has been promoted again.

999
00:45:21,630 --> 00:45:23,900
Ms. Liu truly married the right man.

1000
00:45:24,440 --> 00:45:26,220
All unrelated persons, out of the way!
